Great for single or multi-cat homes, the whole system mounts easily with the included hardware.

purchase_history.item_name: KidCo Stairway Gate Installation Kit
purchase_history.item_desc: Mount any gate easily and damage-free with the KidCo Stairway Gate Installation Kit. Different homes use different designs and materials for stairways, which makes the installation of safety gates difficult since the “one size fits all” gate design does not exist. And so this installation kit offers the solution, with all the materials and fasteners needed to properly install any child safety gate to stairway banisters—and without drilling into your expensive, beautiful wood. Great for use at the top or bottom of the stairs, one kit is required for each side of the gate that is being mounted to the banister.

purchase_history.item_name: OneTigris Tactical Training Molle Vest Dog Harness
purchase_history.item_desc: The OneTigris Tactical Training Molle Vest Dog Harness lets you get into the wild with your adventurous pup while keeping him safe and comfortable. This durable, versatile harness is made with a heavy-duty nylon shell and soft breathable mesh interior padding for ideal comfort on any outing, and also features dual extra-strong V-ring leash loops at the front and rear of the harness. Convenient MOLLE (Modular Lightweight Load-carrying Equipment) webbing along both sides of the harness accepts a wide variety of molle pouches so your canine companion can carry his own supplies. The padded neck strap and dual chest and belly straps provide a snug, secure and comfortable fit, while the fuzzy fastener-style panel along the top allows you to attach an array of morale patches and badges to customize the harness to fit your pup’s style and express his individual personality.

purchase_history.item_name: PetAg Boundary Indoor/Outdoor Cat Repellent
purchase_history.item_desc: Keep cats out of no-go areas with PetAg’s Boundary Indoor/Outdoor Cat Repellent. Repel felines from trees, shrubs, planting beds, garbage cans, furniture or other forbidden areas where a cat’s presence or scent marking is not desired. Simply spray daily until cats get the message!

purchase_history.item_name: Top Performance Natural Flea & Tick Dog & Cat Shampoo
purchase_history.item_desc: Send uninvited hitchhikers on their way with Top Performance Natural Flea & Tick Dog Shampoo. This environmentally friendly formula is designed to naturally rid your furry friend of pesky fleas and ticks, sparing your pet from harsh chemicals and pyrethrin-based pesticides that are commonly found in other remedies. The shampoo features a fresh herbal scent and includes ingredients like aloe, lanolin, lecithin and vitamin E antioxidants to help condition and moisturize your best bud’s skin as it works to prevent future reinfestation.

purchase_history.item_name: Chewy Louie 12" Bully Stick Dog Treat
purchase_history.item_desc: Give your paw-tner a reward he’s sure to appreciate with Chewy Louie’s 12” Bully Stick Dog Treats! These all-natural, single-ingredient chews are crafted with 100% beef from grass-fed cattle. They are completely grain-free, gluten-free, high in protein and low in calories for a guilt-free snack you can feel good about giving your pup. Not only are these treats nutritious, but they are also delicious, offering your sidekick the meaty taste he loves. Paw-fect for moderate chewers, these sticks help encourage healthy teeth and gums by scraping away plaque and tartar as he chews. And because your dog’s treats should be as true as the bond you share, you won’t find any artificial colors, flavors or preservatives here!

purchase_history.item_name: Tucson Bird Designs Peanut Bird Feeder
purchase_history.item_desc: Invite all the beaked buddies in your neighborhood to go nuts with the Tucson Bird Designs Peanut Bird Feeder. It’s specially designed for clinging birds such as woodpeckers, wrens, thrashers, mockingbirds and nuthatches. Offering peanuts to nut-eating birds is economical because the little chirpers have to work hard to pull pieces of the peanuts out. This also makes your wingmen stay on the feeder longer, giving you more time to enjoy the view.

purchase_history.item_name: PetRageous Designs Corbin's Cable Knitted Dog & Cat Sweater
purchase_history.item_desc: **Remember to measure your pet for the paw-fect fit.** Keep your furry friend cozy and stylish this winter with the PetRageous Designs Corbin's Cable Knitted Dog & Cat Sweater. This adorable fisherman-style sweater is made with flecked yarn and includes a fold-down, shawl-style collar with a decorative frog-clasp button for a fashionable twist on cold weather pet comfort. Your dog or cat will stay toasty warm during any outdoor adventure the two of you take part in this winter, thanks to the heavy gauge construction helping to block the chilly winds. And with a pullover, easy-on design that offers ample space, getting your precious pet dressed has never been easier or more comfortable for either of you. Plus, a European cut at the belly helps to keep your fur baby clean and dry during potty breaks.

M-T-G has successfully treated rain rot, dew poisoning, scratches, mud fever, greasy heel, sweet itch, girth itch, itchy skin, dandruff and tail rubbing, and it’s also been used on thrush and white line disease. At 38 inches tall, this comfy kitty condo is the perfect space for your little one to stretch, jump and play to their heart's content. Durable natural sisal feels great on the paws and encourages kitties to scratch—keeping your couches and drapes safe from wayward claws! Multiple perches offer the perfect lounging and basking spots while a fun swing toy inspires playtime and motivates even lethargic kitties to get active. Plus, this all-in-one cat tree and scratching post also features a cozy kitty cave, so your little one can hunker down in safety and seclusion whenever they need a break.

purchase_history.item_name: Earthborn Holistic Wild Sea Catch Grain-Free Natural Dry Cat & Kitten Food
purchase_history.item_desc: Give your kitty the holistic nutrition he needs to thrive with the Earthborn Holistic Wild Sea Catch Grain-Free Natural Dry Cat & Kitten Food. The formula provides plenty of protein to fuel all those adventures and growth spurts, with highly-digestible salmon and herring meals as the top ingredients. Every crunchy bite is loaded with veggies and fruits like blueberries, spinach, apples, and cranberries, plus all the nutrients your pal needs to look and feel his best, like vitamins, omegas, taurine, and probiotics, not to mention the flavor he’ll find irresistible! With no grains, gluten or anything artificial, kitties with sensitivities can dive into the bowl, too.

purchase_history.item_name: Ortho Home Defense Flying Bug Killer with Essential Oils Spray, 14-oz bottle
purchase_history.item_desc: Get flying insects to bug off to the bug afterlife with Ortho Home Defense Flying Bug Killer with Essential Oils. This essential oil-powered formula kills indoor and outdoor flying bugs in seconds with just an easy spray. Shoot the winged menaces mid-flight or spray them where they land, the fast-acting formula will stop them for good! It’s completely safe for use around children and pets and doesn’t have that nasty chemical bug spray smell.

purchase_history.item_name: Castor & Pollux Natural Ultramix Indoor Adult Formula Dry Cat Food
purchase_history.item_desc: Ideal for adult indoor cats and adult cats with low activity levels or a little extra weight, through their senior years. Cats are obligate carnivores, which is a fancy way of saying they need and crave animal-based proteins in their diet. This cutting edge formula contains Castor & Pollux's proprietary Carnivore Health Boost kibble. These dark, hearty, grain-free bits contain multiple sources of animal-based protein - natural chicken, turkey and salmon – that deliver essential nutrition. They then blend these special Carnivore Health Boost bits with a second carefully crafted kibble to create a complete, balanced (and tasty) diet for your cat. Natural Ultramix Adult Indoor Cat Food contains no artificial colors or preservatives, and no corn, wheat or soy.

purchase_history.item_name: KOPEKS Waterproof Quilted Car Seat Cover
purchase_history.item_desc: Make road trips as easy as a walk in the park with the KOPEKS Waterproof Quilted Car Seat Cover. A convenient way to protect your vehicle's back seat from tears, scrapes, dirt and water, this quilted cover will keep it looking like new—and your furry pet will be ecstatic to go along for the ride. Setup is a breeze thanks to the heavy-duty headrest straps, which can be attached to the backseat headrests, or to the front seat's, to create a barrier. And with seat positioning anchors and non-slip rubber backing, you can rest assured that it will stay in place even during sudden stops.

purchase_history.item_name: Royal Canin Size Health Nutrition Giant Puppy Dry Dog Food
purchase_history.item_desc: Serve up the targeted nutrition your puppy deserves with Royal Canin Size Health Nutrition Giant Breed Dry Puppy Food. This extra-large breed puppy food formula features a crunchy puppy kibble texture your big boy will love. Not only that, but the complete and balanced dry dog food is designed to meet your large pup’s unique nutritional needs from 2 to 8 months to support this intense growth stage and control excess weight gain. DHA and omega-3 fatty acid help with your furbaby’s brain development as he goes through his puppy training stage. Antioxidants such as vitamins E and C help with immune support, and a combination of prebiotics and highly digestible proteins promotes healthy digestion. Plus, a specialized blend of minerals provides bone and joint support. Promote your puppy’s overall wellness with every Royal Canin Giant Breed Dry Puppy Food serving.

purchase_history.item_name: Outback Jack Happy Habitat Cat Playpen Tent
purchase_history.item_desc: Give your kitty a breath of fresh air with the Outback Jack Happy Habitat. The safe way to bring your indoor cat into the great outdoors, this handy little tent provides over 30 square feet of fun in the sun. It sets up easy with no tools, and it folds tightly into a convenient carry bag—meaning finally your cat can go wherever you go. Allowing them to maintain their natural instincts yet stay totally safe, it’s the best of both worlds. Great for your backyard, patio or porch, it comes with everything you need to let the outdoor bonding begin.

purchase_history.item_name: Galapagos Royal Pillow Moss Reptile & Amphibian Terrarium Moss, Fresh Green
purchase_history.item_desc: Does your tropical or forest terrarium have style? Take it from basement apartment to tropical penthouse with this Galapagos Royal Pillow Moss. In addition to being lush and lovely to look at, this pillow moss helps maintain the humidity in your terrarium and provides a perfect hideout for your snakes and other critters. Perfect for Eastern newts, fire-bellied newts, dart frogs, tiger salamanders, frogs and toads, pythons, snakes and other similar species. Comes in a resealable bag to help preserve freshness. This is also great for use with tortoises, terrestrial turtles, aquatic amphibians, terrestrial amphibians, invertebrates, lizards, and snakes.
